name: .E48 File Extension
summary: Learn about .E48 files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can open an E48 file in Emu48 (Windows, Android), provided you have already loaded an HP48 graphing calculator ROM image. To do so, select File → Open... from the program's menu bar. Then, navigate to and open your E48 file.
